tags.description: Looking south to the trail, there are signs reading Private Property; No Trespassing. On the south end of this trail are no such signs.
No way around it for pedestrians or bicycles. You can go under it, though, if you lift the chain over you.
Four fixed metal bollards preventing motor vehicles from passing. Also some biycles, unless you lift handlebars or baskets over the bollards.
